author: UPDATE 1-IGC sees global grain supplies at 3-year low on tighter stocks
title: UPDATE 1-IGC sees global grain supplies at 3-year low on tighter stocks
text: *Forecast for wheat, corn output boosted slightly. *Low carryover stocks to lead to tighter supplies. LONDON, May 24- Global grain supplies are poised to fall to a three-year low in the 2018/ 19 season due to a drawdown in stocks coupled with a slight dip in output, the International Grains Council said on Thursday.
